metadata.name: Doze off
metadata.description:
“Doze off” is a part of the “Somewhere not here” , which captures the everyday moments that I thought were wonderful - for example, on holiday afternoons, spending time with friends, spending time alone at a cafe, etc.- and express what I felt during these moments with neon light and abstract objects.

The concept of this piece is the moment when you fell asleep when you are relaxing alone.
